# --------------------------------------------------
# Recursively:
# --------------------------------------------------
# - Archive indicator
# --------------------------------------------------
**/_*
# --------------------------------------------------
# - All swap files
# --------------------------------------------------
**/*.swp
# --------------------------------------------------
# - editor
# --------------------------------------------------
**/.vscode/
**/.claude/
**/.zed/
# --------------------------------------------------
# - Generated files (rust specific)
# --------------------------------------------------
**/target/
**/Cargo.lock
**/*.rs.bk
**/*.pdb
**/*.rustc_info.json
**/*.cargo-ok
**/*CACHEDIR.TAG
# --------------------------------------------------
# vendored
# --------------------------------------------------
vendor
# --------------------------------------------------
# ignore all in `deploy`
# --------------------------------------------------
deploy/*
# --------------------------------------------------
# whitelist `deploy/prod` (submodule)
# --------------------------------------------------
!deploy/prod
